title: Fiasco at India AI Expo: Galgotias University bagged a booth bigger than what 4 IITs combined got
description: The exhibition space at the India AI Impact Expo was leased out on a first-come-first-served basis under the supervision of the Software Technology Parks of India (STPI), with no formal vetting of what these institutions planned to showcase.

title: Global tech leaders call for collective action at the India AI Impact Summit
description: While the world is standing at the precipice of a "once-in-a-generation" shift as artificial intelligence exponentially improves, ensuring that its impact is a net positive to human development will require concerted efforts, global technology leaders said on the fourth day of the India AI Impact Summit here.

title: Aakrit Vaish’s fund Activate ties up with Nvidia to back AI startups
description: Haptik cofounder Aakrit Vaish’s early-stage venture firm Activate has announced a multi-year collaboration with Nvidia to support AI startups in India, with a focus on founders at the idea and pre-company stage.
